  "reference_number": "RUS2544",
  "remarks": "\nIMO 9290921 (“BEAST”) is and has been involved in a relevant activity as it is used for an activity whose object or effect is to destabilise Ukraine or undermine or threaten the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine or to obtain a benefit from or support the Government of Russia. Namely, BEAST is and has been used for carrying oil or oil products that originated in Russia from Russia to a third country. \n",
